<sect2 id="Popup"><title>Popup</title>
<para>
<code>A container that is displayed as a popup. The popup window does not have any special frame. Popups can be displayed when an element is clicked by assigning the id of the popup to either the </code>
<code>XulElement.setPopup(java.lang.String)</code>
<code>, </code>
<code>XulElement.setContext(java.lang.String)</code>
<code> or </code>
<code>XulElement.setTooltip(java.lang.String)</code>
<code> attribute of the element</code>
<code>. </code>
</para>
<para>
<graphic fileref="images/Popup.png"/>
</para>
